{"tid":1801720,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[1月1民陣大遊行] 除咗大遊行 仲有一件事要所有人知道!!!","createTime":"2019-12-29T00:01:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T10:01:43.000Z","uid":249563,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"abba1e69266dab77f6c8917feea73a65cb7f8196","tid":1801720,"uid":249563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:01:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">就係1月1和勇老幼都唔好打尖</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 到底唔打尖有幾重要？<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: navy;\">人數絕非最重要，而係原則問題。</span></strong></span><br />\n適逢新年伊始，香港人更要係1月1號<span style=\"color: green;\">打響頭炮</span>，繼續走上街頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，<strong>如閣下唔經checkpoint行，只會令跟規矩準時喺起點既手足罰企，令遊行屢屢出現水洩不通畫面，但官方最終公佈的數據卻是差強人意。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]即係話你唔經起點行，係無拎到最大既遊行效果，更可能逼走起點苦等嘅人。</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[red]<strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">香港人 進化 不打尖</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\">插隊撚呢個問題再唔改善，下次就唔會有人去維園<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1774616\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1774616</a><br />\n<br />\n1月1 唔鳩企，主動幫手<br />\n1月1 唔屌狗，咪撚玩膠<br />\n1月1 唔陣地，流水行動<br />\n1月1 唔忘記，抗爭到底</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">未竟全功，誓不罷休。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58849e4fb1318252ff346bb46a11e8421dad11fd","tid":1801720,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:01:59.000Z","msg":"官方認證黃色經濟圈有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />D錢係我既<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75fc919a8edac80a418411cd2ce60bf992a2592d","tid":1801720,"uid":300629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:02:27.000Z","msg":"出得蒞行，就唔好貪方便。P推"},{"pid":"d69c9dce98d53f7860de5ccf95231d61a2abbc82","tid":1801720,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:02:41.000Z","msg":"今日晏就有香港人日與夜的集會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a48ef0dbdff50f33a0cd1491205f63385151f73","tid":1801720,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75fc919a8edac80a418411cd2ce60bf992a2592d","tid":1801720,"uid":300629,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:02:27.000Z","msg":"出得蒞行，就唔好貪方便。P推"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:04:07.000Z","msg":"人數非最重要 但公佈人數愈多 對我地愈有利<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ac496eeb25f5b27e96cc12491fd2866cf17161c","tid":1801720,"uid":340116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d69c9dce98d53f7860de5ccf95231d61a2abbc82","tid":1801720,"uid":249563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:02:41.000Z","msg":"今日晏就有香港人日與夜的集會呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:05:17.000Z","msg":"完全無人講 推"},{"pid":"f7453852953bdedfc80231edb6b5660186cd2b48","tid":1801720,"uid":340116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:05:34.000Z","msg":"tui"},{"pid":"082e2695a0777afee9718020cc8a5a65e50725a2","tid":1801720,"uid":340116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:05:46.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"0bcc4a09d4bead870c1989fa4146dd49eaaee659","tid":1801720,"uid":340116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T00:06:44.000Z","msg":"推呀 推到藍絲都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi